channel.title: Either I'm doing something wrong (probably) or
channel.description: Okay, so I'm trying to log into some servers that looked pretty darn cool, right? So I'm surfin' around, and I found some awesome-looking ones. I enter the IP and Port in the little File < New Server/New Port, mmkay? I put it in, and I click log in with the correct password and username. It still says they're down, when the topic clearly says "Up 24/7" or "Online, up and running" and all that stuff. Is there something [i]I'm[/i] doing wrong, or what?
